      • addMedium

        public void addMedium(Medium medium)
        Adds the given medium to this album. Won't have an effect if the medium is already in this album.
        Parameters:
        medium - The medium to be added to this album.
        Postcondition:
        The medium is in the album.

      • removeMedium

        public void removeMedium(Medium medium)
        Removes the given medium from this album. If it was the last in this album, the album will be deleted.
        Parameters:
        medium - The medium to be deleted.
        Postcondition:
        self.mediaList.contains(medium) != true

      • removeLabel

        public void removeLabel()
        Removes the label associated with this Album. If the label was the creator of the album and we're currently not just changing the label, the album will be deleted.
